Yet you, Eighth Ancestor,

278
00:19:53,720 --> 00:19:54,559
today

279
00:19:54,560 --> 00:19:55,839
are using a replica Imperial weapon

280
00:19:55,840 --> 00:19:56,879
to suppress a human Saint Body.

281
00:19:56,880 --> 00:19:57,959
How is that any different?

282
00:20:00,200 --> 00:20:01,799
Our clan's possessions

283
00:20:02,480 --> 00:20:04,559
exist to safeguard our clan's glory.

284
00:20:05,120 --> 00:20:06,359
Our clan's people

285
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:09,439
should also be used for the family's sake.

286
00:20:10,080 --> 00:20:11,759
Moreover, in this current era,

287
00:20:13,200 --> 00:20:15,519
it is the law of the jungle—
the weak are prey to the strong.

288
00:20:18,600 --> 00:20:20,839
If the Ji Family refuses to change,

289
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:24,719
we will eventually be wiped out in this great era.

290
00:20:27,280 --> 00:20:29,039
Haven't the events of the past

291
00:20:29,040 --> 00:20:30,679
been enough to serve as a warning?

292
00:20:31,280 --> 00:20:33,199
So many Great Emperor families

293
00:20:34,080 --> 00:20:37,159
have turned to dust in this great era because they clung to old ways.

294
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:39,119
You all...

295
00:20:41,080 --> 00:20:42,759
are still too young.

296
00:20:45,960 --> 00:20:47,199
If the Ji Family...

297
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:49,719
becomes one that disregards right and wrong,

298
00:20:49,720 --> 00:20:51,799
extinguishes conscience, and preys on the weak,

299
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:54,000
then I

300
00:20:54,640 --> 00:20:55,559
would rather leave.

301
00:20:55,560 --> 00:20:56,560
How ridiculous.

302
00:20:58,240 --> 00:21:00,199
You possess the Origin Spirit Body.

303
00:21:00,760 --> 00:21:02,879
You are a vital asset to the family.

304
00:21:02,880 --> 00:21:04,519
How can we allow you to leave so easily?

305
00:21:05,320 --> 00:21:06,559
Your fate

306
00:21:07,800 --> 00:21:09,599
has been tied to the Ji Family

307
00:21:10,680 --> 00:21:12,239
since the moment you were born.

308
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:14,519
Your destiny is inseparable from ours.

309
00:21:16,280 --> 00:21:17,280
What do you think you're doing?

310
00:21:17,840 --> 00:21:18,759
Let go of me!

311
00:21:18,760 --> 00:21:19,959
I want to find Ye Fan!

312
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:21,920
Eighth Ancestor!

313
00:21:22,480 --> 00:21:23,559
Let go of me!

314
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:27,200
Reporting to the Eighth Ancestor.

315
00:21:27,520 --> 00:21:28,559
All the holy lands and ancient families

316
00:21:28,560 --> 00:21:30,599
have learned that Miss Ziyue possesses
the Origin Spirit Body.

317
00:21:30,600 --> 00:21:31,399
They have already taken action.

318
00:21:31,720 --> 00:21:32,919
It won't be long before

319
00:21:32,920 --> 00:21:34,919
every prodigy in the world comes flocking.

320
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:38,959
Now that the Origin Spirit Body has been exposed,

321
00:21:39,520 --> 00:21:41,199
hiding it is no longer possible.

322
00:21:41,760 --> 00:21:42,760
Instead of concealing it,

323
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:45,279
we might as well fan the flames

324
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:47,239
and let the news spread across the Northern Dipper.

325
00:21:48,120 --> 00:21:50,199
The Origin Spirit Body is extremely rare in this world.

326
00:21:50,720 --> 00:21:52,799
It can merge with the origin of all things

327
00:21:53,080 --> 00:21:55,159
and command every source force for its own use.

328
00:21:55,680 --> 00:21:57,479
Such a precious asset

329
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:59,279
is unfortunately unstable by nature.

330
00:21:59,800 --> 00:22:01,559
It would be best to choose a suitable husband for her.

331
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:03,079
The timing is perfect.

332
00:22:04,040 --> 00:22:06,879
The Ji Family can use this as an opportunity

333
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:09,239
to restore our family's former glory.

334
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:11,719
Miss's marriage is a matter of great importance.

335
00:22:12,480 --> 00:22:13,559
We should ask the Patriarch first

336
00:22:13,920 --> 00:22:15,079
before making any decision.

337
00:22:16,320 --> 00:22:17,999
A great era is approaching,

338
00:22:18,440 --> 00:22:20,839
yet the Ji Family still clings

339
00:22:21,360 --> 00:22:23,279
to outdated rules and conventions,

340
00:22:23,320 --> 00:22:24,919
stuck in the old ways.

341
00:22:26,000 --> 00:22:27,959
For over a hundred thousand years,

342
00:22:28,400 --> 00:22:30,879
has our family ever produced a Great Emperor?

343
00:22:32,680 --> 00:22:33,999
The prodigies of the Eastern Wasteland

344
00:22:34,360 --> 00:22:35,599
are as numerous as carp crossing a river.

345
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:39,119
Eighth Ancestor, why do you only look toward the Northern Plains?

346
00:22:39,720 --> 00:22:41,079
The bright moon

347
00:22:41,080 --> 00:22:44,319
should naturally shine upon the most brilliant Emperor Star of this age.

348
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:47,279
The Northern Plains is a harsh and bitter land,

349
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:50,159
but if they are willing to form an alliance with our Ji Family,

350
00:22:50,160 --> 00:22:52,479
we will spare no effort to support them.

351
00:22:54,640 --> 00:22:55,640
Eighth Ancestor...

352
00:22:55,880 --> 00:22:56,999
With a great era upon us,

353
00:22:57,320 --> 00:22:59,599
having allies will naturally make things much easier.

354
00:22:59,760 --> 00:23:01,399
The Northern Plains is not like the Ji Family.

355
00:23:01,400 --> 00:23:02,599
We do not have ancestral blessings to rely on.

356
00:23:03,280 --> 00:23:05,199
We can only vie for the Emperor's path in this lifetime.

357
00:23:06,240 --> 00:23:07,599
Since the Ji Family has Mingyue,

358
00:23:08,120 --> 00:23:09,679
she should naturally become

359
00:23:09,880 --> 00:23:11,079
the future matriarch of my Wang Family.

360
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:23,319
I told you last time,

361
00:23:24,080 --> 00:23:27,239
this is not a place your Divine Spirit Valley can visit whenever you please.

362
00:23:28,600 --> 00:23:30,439
Young Master is truly heartless.

363
00:23:31,040 --> 00:23:32,319
Right after we finished cooperating,

364
00:23:32,480 --> 00:23:34,599
you already want to discard us?

365
00:23:36,080 --> 00:23:38,679
And here I specially came to inform Young Master

366
00:23:39,160 --> 00:23:40,519
about a secret from ancient times.

367
00:23:42,080 --> 00:23:43,400
Speak.

368
00:23:44,160 --> 00:23:45,679
In the desolate ancient era,

369
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:48,679
the Void Emperor once fought a bloody battle

370
00:23:48,680 --> 00:23:50,639
against a Supreme of my Primordial Race
in the outer starry sky.

371
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:52,599
The Imperial Mirror illuminated ten thousand ages,

372
00:23:52,840 --> 00:23:55,199
and the Imperial Tower could freeze eternity itself.

373
00:23:57,480 --> 00:23:58,519
That battle

374
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:00,759
shattered the galaxy

375
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:03,279
and buried an entire era.

376
00:24:05,800 --> 00:24:07,519
The Supreme ultimately perished,

377
00:24:08,120 --> 00:24:11,399
but the fragments of Eternal Blue Gold stained with the Void Emperor's blood

378
00:24:11,760 --> 00:24:14,919
lie hidden in the deepest part of the Ji Family's Void Ancient Hall.

379
00:24:16,280 --> 00:24:17,999
Guarded by an Imperial formation,

380
00:24:18,800 --> 00:24:20,639
yet also forgotten by it.

381
00:24:26,800 --> 00:24:29,119
And the scripture I used you as bait for earlier

382
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:33,879
can draw upon the supreme laws contained within those fragments.

383
00:24:41,040 --> 00:24:43,839
I know Young Master plans to visit the Ji Family's sacred land.

384
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:46,079
Why not use the marriage alliance as a chance

385
00:24:46,080 --> 00:24:48,039
to personally enter the Void Ancient Hall

386
00:24:48,600 --> 00:24:50,039
and retrieve

387
00:24:50,400 --> 00:24:53,159
the fortune that rightfully belongs to you?

388
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:54,399
An opportunity like this

389
00:24:54,680 --> 00:24:55,919
is invaluable.

390
00:24:57,320 --> 00:24:58,320
Speak.

391
00:24:58,440 --> 00:24:59,440
What do you want?

392
00:25:01,640 --> 00:25:03,479
My race's revival is imminent.

393
00:25:03,920 --> 00:25:05,279
What we need...

394
00:25:05,520 --> 00:25:06,959
Others may not know,

395
00:25:08,040 --> 00:25:09,999
but surely the Northern Emperor understands.

396
00:25:10,960 --> 00:25:12,279
The Origin Spirit Body...

397
00:25:12,720 --> 00:25:14,719
We can share it with the Northern Emperor.

398
00:25:15,320 --> 00:25:16,919
We will also

399
00:25:16,920 --> 00:25:18,759
clear all obstacles for you.

400
00:25:18,783 --> 00:25:38,883
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

401
00:25:39,800 --> 00:25:40,879
This Void Mirror

402
00:25:41,360 --> 00:25:43,759
looks different from the one Ji Haoyue brought out before.

403
00:25:43,960 --> 00:25:45,399
It seems like a replica.

404
00:25:46,040 --> 00:25:48,639
It looks like the Eighth Ancestor can't freely summon
the true Imperial weapon.

405
00:25:57,960 --> 00:25:59,639
Just a replica of the Void Mirror

406
00:26:00,160 --> 00:26:01,439
was enough to wound me this badly.

407
00:26:02,760 --> 00:26:04,119
And that Wang Teng...

408
00:26:04,960 --> 00:26:06,479
No matter what your goal is,

409
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:08,759
I will remember this debt

410
00:26:09,600 --> 00:26:11,079
very clearly.

411
00:26:12,360 --> 00:26:13,519
Forget it.

412
00:26:14,160 --> 00:26:16,239
I must leave this place first.

413
00:26:28,840 --> 00:26:30,679
Looks like Young Master was right.

414
00:26:30,680 --> 00:26:32,679
The Saint Body really isn't that easy to kill.

415
00:26:55,800 --> 00:26:56,800
I never expected

416
00:26:57,040 --> 00:26:58,479
that the mighty human Saint Body

417
00:26:58,480 --> 00:27:00,079
would end up in such a sorry state.

418
00:27:00,120 --> 00:27:01,399
I'm heavily injured.

419
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:03,959
Don't you think it's a bit shameless
to attack me like this?

420
00:27:04,280 --> 00:27:05,719
Times have changed.

421
00:27:06,120 --> 00:27:07,239
You are the fish on the chopping block,

422
00:27:07,240 --> 00:27:08,279
and I am the knife.

423
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:10,759
I'll slice your flesh piece by piece

424
00:27:10,880 --> 00:27:12,799
and let my race's creatures devour every last bit.

425
00:27:13,520 --> 00:27:14,879
Go to hell!

426
00:27:32,240 --> 00:27:33,240
What?

427
00:27:33,400 --> 00:27:34,759
Weren't you heavily injured?

428
00:27:34,760 --> 00:27:36,479
Though I'm heavily injured and exhausted,

429
00:27:37,040 --> 00:27:38,639
the dragon qi in this place is extremely abundant.

430
00:27:38,640 --> 00:27:41,159
It's more than enough to wipe out you two little shrimps.

431
00:27:41,240 --> 00:27:41,759
This is...

432
00:27:41,960 --> 00:27:42,599
Source Arts!

433
00:27:42,600 --> 00:27:44,479
It's too late to realize now.

434
00:27:55,960 --> 00:27:57,119
Don't get trapped by his Source Arts!

435
00:27:57,400 --> 00:27:58,400
Get in close and fight him!

436
00:28:10,920 --> 00:28:11,719
Speak.

437
00:28:11,920 --> 00:28:13,079
Who sent you?

438
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:15,159
Saint Body,

439
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:16,999
your life will be taken sooner or later.

440
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:18,639
Why should we need anyone else's help?

441
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:23,719
I'll talk! I'll talk!

442
00:28:24,320 --> 00:28:26,239
It was the Young Master of Divine Spirit Valley,

443
00:28:26,480 --> 00:28:27,679
Zi Tianfeng.

444
00:28:28,840 --> 00:28:29,840
Zi Tianfeng...

445
00:28:30,160 --> 00:28:31,319
Divine Spirit Valley...

446
00:28:32,720 --> 00:28:34,199
What does killing me benefit her?

447
00:28:34,760 --> 00:28:36,079
She's helping Wang Teng.

448
00:28:36,720 --> 00:28:39,399
She knows you have a close relationship with the Origin Spirit Body.

449
00:28:39,400 --> 00:28:40,400
Killing you

450
00:28:40,520 --> 00:28:42,559
is to clear the path for Wang Teng's marriage alliance with the Ji Family.

451
00:28:42,560 --> 00:28:44,079
To remove all obstacles.

452
00:28:46,880 --> 00:28:47,880
Keep talking.

453
00:28:51,080 --> 00:28:52,319
The Ji Family's Eighth Ancestor

454
00:28:52,720 --> 00:28:53,479
wants to

455
00:28:53,720 --> 00:28:54,720
marry the Origin Spirit Body

456
00:28:56,320 --> 00:28:57,320
to

457
00:28:57,400 --> 00:28:58,559
the Northern Emperor, Wang Teng.

458
00:28:58,880 --> 00:29:00,519
So you must die.

459
00:29:02,440 --> 00:29:03,440
Wang Teng...

460
00:29:03,720 --> 00:29:04,720
Saint Body, we...

461
00:29:05,120 --> 00:29:07,919
We've told you everything we know.

462
00:29:08,880 --> 00:29:10,239
We beg you, Lord Saint Body,

463
00:29:10,360 --> 00:29:11,479
spare our lives!

464
00:29:11,680 --> 00:29:12,680
Spare us!

465
00:29:12,720 --> 00:29:14,799
Lord Saint Body, please spare us!

466
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:17,479
The Ji Family's Eighth Ancestor,

467
00:29:18,640 --> 00:29:20,199
Wang Teng from the Northern Plains,

468
00:29:22,400 --> 00:29:23,759
and Divine Spirit Valley...

469
00:29:24,160 --> 00:29:25,439
Zi Tianfeng.

470
00:29:26,600 --> 00:29:28,399
Three factions working together

471
00:29:29,240 --> 00:29:31,119
just to take my life, Ye Fan.

472
00:29:32,000 --> 00:29:33,319
It's almost too ridiculous to believe.

473
00:29:34,360 --> 00:29:36,639
The most urgent task now is to increase my strength as quickly as possible.

474
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:40,000
That's right.

475
00:29:43,040 --> 00:29:44,439
Since you two are primordial remnants,

476
00:29:45,120 --> 00:29:46,120
and you've already come here,

477
00:29:46,440 --> 00:29:47,919
you might as well help me decipher these ancient runes.

478
00:30:00,000 --> 00:30:00,399
This...

479
00:30:00,600 --> 00:30:01,600
This is...

480
00:30:03,000 --> 00:30:04,639
The Solar True Scripture!

481
00:30:04,920 --> 00:30:06,439
How could he possibly have the Solar True Scripture?

482
00:30:07,760 --> 00:30:09,519
How could such a Great Emperor inheritance

483
00:30:09,840 --> 00:30:11,119
be in your hands?

484
00:30:12,600 --> 00:30:13,600
Could it be...

485
00:30:13,840 --> 00:30:14,840
that you have some connection with that

486
00:30:15,080 --> 00:30:16,999
old devil Dongfang Taiyi?

487
00:30:21,240 --> 00:30:23,039
Since you recognize these scriptures,

488
00:30:24,200 --> 00:30:25,839
then each of you will translate a copy.

489
00:30:27,360 --> 00:30:28,360
But remember this well:

490
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:31,279
If there's even a single character difference

491
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:34,039
in the translated text,

492
00:30:34,240 --> 00:30:35,279
whether I kill you or torture you,

493
00:30:35,360 --> 00:30:36,719
it will be entirely up to me.

494
00:30:46,360 --> 00:30:47,360
Ye Fan...

495
00:30:52,720 --> 00:30:53,759
Lord Saint Body,

496
00:30:54,080 --> 00:30:55,359
the scriptures have been fully translated.

497
00:30:56,040 --> 00:30:57,040
Please review them.

498
00:31:05,480 --> 00:31:07,039
The Solar True Scripture...

499
00:31:11,560 --> 00:31:13,479
It is actually one of the primordial scriptures of the human race.

500
00:31:14,160 --> 00:31:15,160
With this scripture,

501
00:31:15,680 --> 00:31:16,879
I may be able to reach a higher level.

502
00:31:35,480 --> 00:31:36,480
Truly profound.

503
00:31:37,480 --> 00:31:38,959
It washes away all mortal impurities,

504
00:31:39,360 --> 00:31:40,439
refines true yang,

505
00:31:41,040 --> 00:31:42,199
and seizes creation in reverse.

506
00:31:50,200 --> 00:31:51,200
My strange phenomenon

507
00:31:51,400 --> 00:31:52,879
is actually resonating with the Solar True Scripture.

508
00:31:53,840 --> 00:31:55,519
And the divine power far exceeds my current level.

509
00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:05,880
He’s going to...

510
00:32:06,120 --> 00:32:07,239
He’s going to break through!

511
00:33:01,560 --> 00:33:04,119
Congratulations on breaking through and being reborn, Saint Body.

512
00:33:09,040 --> 00:33:10,159
I can let you go,

513
00:33:10,440 --> 00:33:12,199
but you know too much.

514
00:33:12,800 --> 00:33:14,719
I’ll have to erase your memories.

515
00:33:15,240 --> 00:33:17,319
Thank you, Saint Body.

516
00:33:36,040 --> 00:33:37,759
The Saint Body has actually recovered.

517
00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:39,719
For the glory of the Primordial Race,

518
00:33:39,920 --> 00:33:40,920
let’s attack together!

519
00:33:41,520 --> 00:33:42,520
Ye Fan!

520
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:43,879
Die!

521
00:33:48,640 --> 00:33:50,839
You’ve really wasted your hot blood.

522
00:33:58,240 --> 00:34:00,079
Ye Fan is still alive.

523
00:34:01,360 --> 00:34:03,159
Then let little brother handle it.

524
00:34:04,160 --> 00:34:05,799
We need to add more fuel

525
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:07,519
to the fire for our Northern Emperor.

526
00:34:14,400 --> 00:34:17,119
No one else decides my sister’s marriage.

527
00:34:17,600 --> 00:34:18,959
Only she can decide.

528
00:34:19,600 --> 00:34:20,799
What is the meaning of this?

529
00:34:21,280 --> 00:34:22,280
Wang Teng.

530
00:34:22,640 --> 00:34:24,399
I am not one of those who fear you.

531
00:34:25,080 --> 00:34:26,239
Fight me.

532
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:27,920
Come on.

533
00:34:31,240 --> 00:34:33,119
Brother Haoyue, your behavior

534
00:34:34,080 --> 00:34:35,080
is far too improper.

535
00:34:35,680 --> 00:34:37,439
It damages the dignity of the Ji Family.

536
00:34:44,680 --> 00:34:45,680
Haoyue.

537
00:34:49,680 --> 00:34:51,199
This marriage alliance between our families

538
00:34:51,200 --> 00:34:52,679
is for the sake of our Dao lineage’s immortality.

539
00:34:53,400 --> 00:34:54,799
As the Divine Body of the Ji Family,

540
00:34:54,880 --> 00:34:55,399
you should have this awareness.

541
00:34:55,400 --> 00:34:57,159
Did the Eighth Ancestor ever ask Ziyue for her opinion?

542
00:34:57,320 --> 00:34:58,320
Foolish.

543
00:34:58,360 --> 00:35:01,239
Matters of marriage have always been decided by our elders.

544
00:35:01,640 --> 00:35:03,159
How can juniors interfere?

545
00:35:04,280 --> 00:35:05,799
Since I am overseeing clan affairs in his stead,

546
00:35:06,520 --> 00:35:08,319
I must choose for the Ji Family’s brightest pearl

547
00:35:08,680 --> 00:35:10,519
the strongest husband of this era.

548
00:35:12,320 --> 00:35:13,320
Everyone,

549
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:15,799
allow this old man to ask:

550
00:35:16,720 --> 00:35:17,999
Among the younger generation,

551
00:35:18,360 --> 00:35:20,639
who is currently unrivaled in the world?

552
00:35:20,840 --> 00:35:21,959
Who is qualified

553
00:35:22,240 --> 00:35:24,279
to match our Ji Family’s brightest pearl?

554
00:35:28,960 --> 00:35:30,199
My Teng’er

555
00:35:30,240 --> 00:35:31,959
possesses the bearing of a Great Emperor.

556
00:35:32,560 --> 00:35:34,239
He wields the Chaos Ancient Emperor Scripture.

557
00:35:34,760 --> 00:35:35,760
In his generation,

558
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:37,119
who can rival him?

559
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:38,800
In terms of qualifications,

560
00:35:39,520 --> 00:35:40,719
no one can compare.

561
00:35:42,200 --> 00:35:43,759
We have not yet fought.

562
00:35:43,960 --> 00:35:45,279
How can you claim to be unrivaled among your peers?

563
00:35:45,760 --> 00:35:47,719
Defeat me first, then we’ll talk.

564
00:35:49,600 --> 00:35:50,600
Brother Haoyue,

565
00:35:51,160 --> 00:35:52,639
we will soon be family.

566
00:35:52,920 --> 00:35:54,199
It would be a shame to ruin our relationship.

567
00:35:54,200 --> 00:35:55,799
Your sister would be heartbroken.

568
00:35:56,640 --> 00:35:58,599
But if you insist on provoking me,

569
00:35:58,600 --> 00:35:59,799
then come and fight.

570
00:36:00,320 --> 00:36:01,599
Never losing is my Dao.

571
00:36:01,600 --> 00:36:02,879
Northern Emperor, please calm yourself.

572
00:36:04,720 --> 00:36:06,159
Since the Patriarch has not come out of seclusion,

573
00:36:06,360 --> 00:36:08,439
whoever can pass the trial of the Ancient Hall

574
00:36:08,760 --> 00:36:10,879
shall be the one to marry our clan’s Mingyue.

575
00:36:12,040 --> 00:36:14,199
As for whether you are qualified,

576
00:36:14,760 --> 00:36:16,319
why not let

577
00:36:16,600 --> 00:36:19,399
our clan’s Void Emperor decide the answer?

578
00:36:26,160 --> 00:36:27,160
Wang Teng.

579
00:36:27,360 --> 00:36:28,599
I am willing to enter the Ancient Hall and take the trial.

580
00:36:30,680 --> 00:36:31,159
Teng’er...

581
00:36:31,560 --> 00:36:31,919
You...

582
00:36:32,480 --> 00:36:33,480
Good.

583
00:36:34,120 --> 00:36:36,399
If you can make the Ancient Hall resonate,

584
00:36:36,800 --> 00:36:39,799
you will be the heaven-chosen one personally selected by our clan’s Great Emperor.

585
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:42,239
As for the marriage with Ziyue,

586
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:44,199
no one in the entire Ji Family

587
00:36:44,480 --> 00:36:45,799
will be able to stop it.

588
00:36:46,720 --> 00:36:47,720
Of course,

589
00:36:48,760 --> 00:36:49,919
if you fail...

590
00:36:49,920 --> 00:36:50,920
Fail?

591
00:36:52,600 --> 00:36:54,559
I have obtained the Chaos Ancient Great Emperor’s inheritance

592
00:36:55,480 --> 00:36:56,799
and hold the Nine Secrets in my hands.

593
00:36:57,440 --> 00:36:58,999
I am a bearer of great destiny in this era.

594
00:36:59,520 --> 00:37:00,520
How could I possibly fail?

595
00:37:27,440 --> 00:37:29,159
There are countless human prodigies.

596
00:37:29,480 --> 00:37:30,759
Why does it have to be Wang Teng?

597
00:37:32,400 --> 00:37:33,959
This child’s edge is too sharp.

598
00:37:34,280 --> 00:37:35,519
He may be difficult to control.

599
00:37:37,120 --> 00:37:38,359
As long as he

600
00:37:38,600 --> 00:37:39,759
enters the Ji Family,

601
00:37:40,480 --> 00:37:43,279
our task will already be complete.

602
00:37:44,120 --> 00:37:45,639
As for the Saint Body...

603
00:38:33,040 --> 00:38:34,559
Ye Fan.

604
00:38:41,480 --> 00:38:42,559
You’ve lost.

605
00:38:52,160 --> 00:38:53,160
This is...

606
00:38:57,680 --> 00:38:59,079
The Divine Son thinks

607
00:39:00,160 --> 00:39:01,719
the Saint Body

608
00:39:02,120 --> 00:39:03,120
will come this time?

609
00:39:03,200 --> 00:39:04,200
Soon.

610
00:39:04,520 --> 00:39:05,519
It would be good if Wang Teng wins,

611
00:39:05,520 --> 00:39:06,679
of course.

612
00:39:07,080 --> 00:39:08,759
But if he loses...

613
00:39:27,520 --> 00:39:28,799
Sister Ziyue

614
00:39:29,320 --> 00:39:30,599
has been taken back to the Ji Family.

615
00:39:31,840 --> 00:39:34,559
[Jiang Tingting — Ancient Jiang Clan]
The clan elders say she’s about to be married off soon.

616
00:39:35,720 --> 00:39:36,399
Big Brother...

617
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:38,399
Why hasn’t he come back yet?

618
00:39:40,920 --> 00:39:41,920
Tingting.

619
00:39:42,760 --> 00:39:43,760
Don’t worry.

620
00:39:45,000 --> 00:39:46,000
Maybe

621
00:39:46,280 --> 00:39:47,679
Big Brother is just nearby

622
00:39:48,120 --> 00:39:49,439
and will come find us any moment now.

623
00:39:59,200 --> 00:39:59,879
Yezi...

624
00:40:00,600 --> 00:40:01,679
Why haven’t you come back yet?

625
00:40:03,440 --> 00:40:04,679
That bastard Ji Family

626
00:40:05,040 --> 00:40:06,919
actually wants to marry Ji Ziyue to Wang Teng.

627
00:40:07,200 --> 00:40:08,479
Isn’t that just to spite you?

628
00:40:10,240 --> 00:40:11,319
Hurry back...

629
00:40:12,200 --> 00:40:13,599
Still waiting, huh?

630
00:40:18,280 --> 00:40:19,280
Stop waiting.

631
00:40:19,520 --> 00:40:21,199
That Ye guy is already dead.

632
00:40:21,320 --> 00:40:22,599
Yet you’re still deluding yourself.

633
00:40:22,600 --> 00:40:23,879
You Wang Family little bastard.

634
00:40:24,080 --> 00:40:25,080
What did you just say?

635
00:40:27,440 --> 00:40:28,839
You still don’t know?

636
00:40:33,080 --> 00:40:34,159
Well, I guess not.

637
00:40:34,800 --> 00:40:36,079
His body

638
00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:39,519
was completely devoured by the Primordial Race.

639
00:40:39,520 --> 00:40:40,839
Not even bones were left.

640
00:40:41,960 --> 00:40:43,239
Inside Purple Mountain,

641
00:40:43,440 --> 00:40:46,159
his saint blood is scattered everywhere.

642
00:40:46,520 --> 00:40:47,639
You’re courting death!

643
00:40:56,120 --> 00:40:57,519
Little girl,

644
00:40:57,880 --> 00:40:59,359
your Sister Ziyue

645
00:40:59,640 --> 00:41:00,640
will soon

646
00:41:00,760 --> 00:41:02,639
be given to my brother.

647
00:41:03,280 --> 00:41:04,799
And now I’ll send you down

648
00:41:05,160 --> 00:41:06,639
to accompany your Big Brother.

649
00:41:06,640 --> 00:41:08,359
You little bastard!

650
00:41:08,680 --> 00:41:10,199
I’ll crush you to death!

651
00:41:10,200 --> 00:41:11,200
Still don’t believe it?

652
00:41:12,280 --> 00:41:13,280
Kneel!

653
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:21,279
Wang Family...

654
00:41:21,960 --> 00:41:23,319
bastard.

655
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:26,359
Quite the tough guy.

656
00:41:27,240 --> 00:41:29,239
I was planning to send you all invitations,

657
00:41:29,840 --> 00:41:30,919
but now

658
00:41:31,400 --> 00:41:32,919
I’ve changed my mind.

659
00:41:34,240 --> 00:41:37,679
I’ll skin you all alive, rip out your tendons,
and turn you into lanterns.

660
00:41:38,080 --> 00:41:39,080
Then place them

661
00:41:39,120 --> 00:41:40,639
at the wedding venue

662
00:41:41,760 --> 00:41:43,279
so you can witness

663
00:41:43,880 --> 00:41:46,719
the grand spectacle of my Wang Family marrying the Origin Spirit Body.

664
00:41:47,400 --> 00:41:48,639
Go down and tell Ye Fan

665
00:41:49,120 --> 00:41:50,159
that his woman

666
00:41:50,560 --> 00:41:51,879
has been graciously accepted by my brother.

667
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:03,199
It’s the Mother Qi Cauldron of All Things!

668
00:42:04,000 --> 00:42:04,639
Yezi!

669
00:42:04,880 --> 00:42:05,880
Big Brother!

670
00:42:06,840 --> 00:42:07,840
Yezi!

671
00:42:07,864 --> 00:42:17,264
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

672
00:42:18,000 --> 00:42:19,000
Big Brother!

673
00:42:29,640 --> 00:42:30,640
Young Master!

674
00:42:30,680 --> 00:42:31,479
Young Master!

675
00:42:31,480 --> 00:42:32,480
Are you alright?

676
00:42:37,960 --> 00:42:39,039
You’re not dead...

677
00:42:39,320 --> 00:42:40,320
Impossible.

678
00:42:40,480 --> 00:42:41,799
That woman lied to me!

679
00:42:42,080 --> 00:42:43,199
Weren’t you eaten?

680
00:42:43,960 --> 00:42:45,119
Looks like I’m not dead.

681
00:42:45,480 --> 00:42:46,519
You seem very disappointed.

682
00:42:47,440 --> 00:42:48,799
But don’t be too disappointed,

683
00:42:49,280 --> 00:42:50,280
because

684
00:42:50,560 --> 00:42:51,959
you’re all going to die.

685
00:43:04,520 --> 00:43:05,879
The aura on him...

686
00:43:07,920 --> 00:43:09,119
It feels different from before.

687
00:43:09,920 --> 00:43:10,920
Perfect.

688
00:43:11,720 --> 00:43:12,720
Yezi,

689
00:43:12,880 --> 00:43:14,199
kill that little bastard first,

690
00:43:14,440 --> 00:43:15,599
then we’ll deal with his brother.

691
00:43:26,400 --> 00:43:28,399
Even an Immortal Platform Saint Body isn’t that strong, huh?

692
00:43:31,520 --> 00:43:32,679
Ancestral Dragon Seal!

693
00:44:01,480 --> 00:44:02,480
So strong...

694
00:44:02,520 --> 00:44:03,919
You could have killed me in an instant.

695
00:44:03,920 --> 00:44:04,559
Why...

696
00:44:04,760 --> 00:44:05,760
Because

697
00:44:06,440 --> 00:44:09,039
I wanted you to enjoy the beating
before you die.

698
00:44:19,560 --> 00:44:20,560
Big Brother...

699
00:44:22,160 --> 00:44:23,160
Yezi!

700
00:44:23,560 --> 00:44:24,560
Yezi!

701
00:44:25,000 --> 00:44:26,199
I knew you wouldn’t die.

702
00:44:28,320 --> 00:44:29,320
Tell me,

703
00:44:29,360 --> 00:44:30,360
what’s our plan next?

704
00:44:30,400 --> 00:44:31,879
Do we storm the Ji Family to crash the wedding first,

705
00:44:32,160 --> 00:44:35,239
then chop up those Ji Family bastards and Wang Teng together?

706
00:44:36,280 --> 00:44:36,879
No crashing.

707
00:44:37,120 --> 00:44:37,679
But...

708
00:44:39,480 --> 00:44:41,039
I will go ask Ziyue in person

709
00:44:41,160 --> 00:44:43,519
whether she truly wants to marry Wang Teng.

710
00:44:44,640 --> 00:44:45,640
What?

711
00:44:46,440 --> 00:44:47,679
Isn’t that still crashing the wedding?

712
00:44:49,040 --> 00:44:50,759
But the Ji Family has Imperial weapons guarding them.

713
00:44:51,080 --> 00:44:52,639
You’re really going in empty-handed?

714
00:44:52,760 --> 00:44:53,760
That’s why

715
00:44:54,240 --> 00:44:56,719
I need enough trump cards first.

716
00:45:23,920 --> 00:45:25,319
A Great Emperor’s relic.

717
00:45:26,040 --> 00:45:28,079
It bears Imperial blood.

718
00:45:28,520 --> 00:45:30,119
The Great Emperor has chosen him.

719
00:45:33,120 --> 00:45:34,439
He...

720
00:45:34,440 --> 00:45:35,839
is the heaven-chosen one

721
00:45:36,080 --> 00:45:37,399
of my Ji Family.

722
00:45:37,600 --> 00:45:38,999
My son Wang Teng

723
00:45:39,720 --> 00:45:41,959
possesses the bearing of a Great Emperor.

724
00:45:41,960 --> 00:45:48,199
The bearing of a Great Emperor...

725
00:45:53,520 --> 00:45:54,119
Eighth Ancestor.

726
00:45:54,120 --> 00:45:55,120
Speak.

727
00:45:58,200 --> 00:45:59,200
What?

728
00:46:07,880 --> 00:46:08,799
Who did this?

729
00:46:09,960 --> 00:46:11,119
By the time we arrived,

730
00:46:11,320 --> 00:46:12,679
the culprit had already vanished without a trace.

731
00:46:28,240 --> 00:46:29,240
Chong’er...

732
00:46:29,480 --> 00:46:31,199
My Chong’er...

733
00:46:33,120 --> 00:46:33,759
Chong’er!

734
00:46:34,120 --> 00:46:34,839
How could you...

735
00:46:35,280 --> 00:46:36,280
How could you...

736
00:46:36,560 --> 00:46:38,279
Who did this to you?

737
00:46:38,280 --> 00:46:39,280
Ye Fan...

738
00:46:40,920 --> 00:46:42,319
He’s still alive.

739
00:46:43,680 --> 00:46:44,879
My condolences, worthy nephew.

740
00:46:46,000 --> 00:46:47,599
The marriage alliance between our families

741
00:46:47,600 --> 00:46:49,039
is the general trend.

742
00:46:49,040 --> 00:46:50,040
No one can stop it.

743
00:46:50,800 --> 00:46:51,800
In that case,

744
00:46:52,600 --> 00:46:54,039
this old man will arrange for you

745
00:46:54,280 --> 00:46:55,639
to become engaged to Ziyue

746
00:46:55,640 --> 00:46:56,640
in three days.

747
00:46:57,000 --> 00:46:58,519
If that little thief dares to come,

748
00:47:00,560 --> 00:47:02,359
I will extinguish him once more.

749
00:47:08,600 --> 00:47:09,600
Chong’er...

750
00:47:10,000 --> 00:47:11,239
Zi Tianfeng...

751
00:47:11,880 --> 00:47:12,999
No matter what,

752
00:47:13,440 --> 00:47:14,999
Ye Fan, you are dead for sure.

753
00:48:30,040 --> 00:48:31,799
This time when I go to the Ji Family to face their Imperial weapons,

754
00:48:32,520 --> 00:48:34,119
the Nine-colored Divine Flame of the Fire Domain,

755
00:48:34,440 --> 00:48:36,319
and the bronze little coffin from the Desolate Ancient Forbidden Land

756
00:48:37,280 --> 00:48:39,239
will be my greatest support.

757
00:49:17,080 --> 00:49:19,399
The demon race’s Imperial weapon and the Heaven Swallowing Demon Jar...

758
00:49:19,680 --> 00:49:21,279
How is the investigation going?

759
00:49:24,680 --> 00:49:26,519
The old blind man and the Peacock King

760
00:49:26,680 --> 00:49:28,519
have both sealed themselves in seclusion,
guarded by Imperial weapons.

761
00:49:29,400 --> 00:49:30,400
The Saint Body

762
00:49:30,440 --> 00:49:31,559
has no way to borrow them.

763
00:49:33,400 --> 00:49:34,439
Patriarch Wang.

764
00:49:35,120 --> 00:49:36,359
Greetings, greetings.

765
00:49:36,840 --> 00:49:37,840
Please, come inside.

766
00:49:41,800 --> 00:49:42,800
Good.

767
00:49:43,080 --> 00:49:44,799
As long as there is no Extreme Dao Imperial weapon,

768
00:49:45,120 --> 00:49:46,679
on Ji Family territory,

769
00:49:47,120 --> 00:49:48,359
the Saint Body

770
00:49:48,800 --> 00:49:50,719
will surely bleed across our sacred land.

771
00:49:53,000 --> 00:49:55,439
The Ji Family has survived until now,

772
00:49:55,960 --> 00:49:58,399
but our foundation has already suffered heavy losses.

773
00:49:58,880 --> 00:50:00,919
If we do not produce a Great Emperor soon,

774
00:50:01,080 --> 00:50:02,919
what future does our clan have?

775
00:50:03,760 --> 00:50:06,239
Rather than pinning our hopes on the younger generation,

776
00:50:06,240 --> 00:50:07,959
it is better to rely on ourselves.

777
00:50:08,760 --> 00:50:10,239
At present,

778
00:50:10,520 --> 00:50:12,479
a marriage alliance seems the most reliable path.

779
00:50:19,520 --> 00:50:20,520
Miss,

780
00:50:20,640 --> 00:50:21,599
the auspicious hour is approaching.

781
00:50:22,120 --> 00:50:23,519
Does the ceremonial robe fit well?

782
00:50:34,160 --> 00:50:36,279
We respectfully welcome the Northern Emperor.

783
00:50:57,760 --> 00:50:58,760
I’m so anxious.

784
00:50:59,400 --> 00:51:00,759
Why hasn’t Brother Ye arrived yet?

785
00:51:01,160 --> 00:51:02,160
Don’t worry.

786
00:51:02,320 --> 00:51:03,599
He will definitely come.

787
00:51:30,400 --> 00:51:32,399
Qian Yuan opens fortune.

788
00:51:32,640 --> 00:51:34,559
The auspicious hour is upon us.

789
00:51:35,160 --> 00:51:37,999
Today, the Ji Family’s direct daughter, Ziyue,

790
00:51:38,520 --> 00:51:41,439
shall follow the Azure Luan bearing the sash ceremony

791
00:51:42,080 --> 00:51:45,119
to fulfill the Black Tortoise alliance pact.

792
00:51:46,080 --> 00:51:47,080
Please.

793
00:51:47,960 --> 00:51:50,239
The phoenix carriage departs the pavilion.

794
00:52:43,400 --> 00:52:44,959
This is utterly improper!

795
00:52:47,080 --> 00:52:48,080
Eighth Ancestor,

796
00:52:48,680 --> 00:52:50,439
what is the meaning of this?

797
00:52:52,320 --> 00:52:53,320
Ziyue...

798
00:52:54,200 --> 00:52:56,119
You must not disregard the greater good.

799
00:52:56,120 --> 00:52:57,319
This is my big day.

800
00:52:58,200 --> 00:53:00,119
Of course I’ll wear what I want.

801
00:53:03,520 --> 00:53:04,520
Young Master of the Wang Family,

802
00:53:05,200 --> 00:53:06,399
do you recognize this pattern?

803
00:53:06,880 --> 00:53:08,079
These cloud-brocade motifs

804
00:53:08,720 --> 00:53:10,319
are the Spirit Raft Flower of the Eastern Wasteland.

805
00:53:10,960 --> 00:53:12,199
They symbolize breaking free from bonds

806
00:53:12,240 --> 00:53:13,759
and roaming the starry river.

807
00:53:13,920 --> 00:53:14,920
Their flower language

808
00:53:15,520 --> 00:53:16,559
means longing,

809
00:53:17,360 --> 00:53:18,360
and also freedom.

810
00:53:18,960 --> 00:53:19,960
Someone come!

811
00:53:20,600 --> 00:53:21,959
Take the young miss back to her room to change.

812
00:53:21,960 --> 00:53:22,999
I’ve thought about it carefully.

813
00:53:23,560 --> 00:53:24,919
I’ve accepted everything the family has given me,

814
00:53:25,200 --> 00:53:27,359
so it’s only right that I contribute in return.

815
00:53:28,080 --> 00:53:29,080
But

816
00:53:29,200 --> 00:53:30,999
does contributing only mean marrying someone?

817
00:53:31,800 --> 00:53:33,279
My Origin Spirit Body can help him achieve the Dao,

818
00:53:33,800 --> 00:53:35,559
but if Wang Teng fails to become a Great Emperor in the future,

819
00:53:35,720 --> 00:53:37,759
wouldn’t that ruin my own chances of becoming one?

820
00:53:38,240 --> 00:53:38,839
Besides,

821
00:53:39,560 --> 00:53:41,639
who can guarantee he hasn’t colluded with the Primordial Race?

822
00:53:42,200 --> 00:53:43,200
Foolish girl.

823
00:53:43,240 --> 00:53:45,239
Female Great Emperors have always been rare.

824
00:53:45,480 --> 00:53:46,359
And what does this have to do with the Primordial Race?

825
00:53:46,360 --> 00:53:48,079
Didn’t the Ruthless also become known as a female emperor?

826
00:53:48,640 --> 00:53:49,640
The Primordial Race

827
00:53:49,760 --> 00:53:52,079
naturally wants the Origin Spirit Body to speed up their revival.

828
00:53:52,520 --> 00:53:53,520
Even if I’m wrong,

829
00:53:53,720 --> 00:53:55,879
I still refuse to sacrifice myself for your so-called greater good.

830
00:53:56,160 --> 00:53:57,199
Your greater good...

831
00:53:57,360 --> 00:53:58,799
Why does it always come at someone else’s expense?

832
00:53:58,800 --> 00:53:59,800
Take her away.

833
00:54:00,480 --> 00:54:01,480
Put the ceremonial robe on her.

834
00:54:02,520 --> 00:54:04,119
If she dares resist again,

835
00:54:04,360 --> 00:54:05,599
punish her according to clan law.

836
00:54:12,040 --> 00:54:13,040
What’s happening?

837
00:54:16,000 --> 00:54:17,279
Ye Fan...

838
00:54:17,840 --> 00:54:19,759
You’ve finally come.

839
00:54:22,280 --> 00:54:23,239
It’s Ye Fan’s aura.

840
00:54:23,880 --> 00:54:26,039
Someone must have brought an unparalleled secret treasure

841
00:54:26,240 --> 00:54:28,039
and triggered the Emperor’s residual formation patterns.

842
00:54:35,160 --> 00:54:36,160
Who goes there?

843
00:54:40,400 --> 00:54:41,400
Ye...

844
00:54:42,080 --> 00:54:43,080
Fan.

845
00:55:37,160 --> 00:55:38,160
Ye Fan!

846
00:55:42,920 --> 00:55:44,239
Everyone from the Wang Family, hear this!

847
00:55:44,760 --> 00:55:46,239
How dare you come here and provoke us!

848
00:56:17,680 --> 00:56:18,680
Ye Fan.

849
00:56:20,440 --> 00:56:21,440
Ziyue.

850
00:56:22,440 --> 00:56:24,359
I heard someone forced you into an engagement.

851
00:56:25,840 --> 00:56:27,239
I’ve come to free you from that burden.

852
00:56:28,760 --> 00:56:30,319
Just shake your head and refuse.

853
00:56:30,840 --> 00:56:31,999
Today, I’ll take you away.

854
00:56:32,280 --> 00:56:33,679
No one will stop us.

855
00:56:38,240 --> 00:56:38,879
Ziyue.

856
00:56:41,040 --> 00:56:42,279
Do you agree?

857
00:56:42,720 --> 00:56:43,999
Of course I don’t.

858
00:56:49,640 --> 00:56:50,640
Very well.

859
00:56:54,080 --> 00:56:55,559
Then I’ll cut him down.

860
00:56:56,480 --> 00:56:57,480
Ye Fan.

861
00:56:58,120 --> 00:56:59,679
I knew you would come today.

862
00:57:00,720 --> 00:57:02,559
Today I will use your saint blood

863
00:57:03,160 --> 00:57:05,199
to honor Chong’er’s spirit in heaven.

864
00:57:06,160 --> 00:57:09,519
An Emperor’s path without your corpse
would be too lonely and incomplete.

865
00:57:09,960 --> 00:57:11,079
So in this battle,

866
00:57:11,640 --> 00:57:13,039
I must thank you for making it possible.

867
00:57:13,040 --> 00:57:14,040
Wang Teng.

868
00:57:14,680 --> 00:57:16,239
You claim to possess the bearing of a Great Emperor,

869
00:57:16,760 --> 00:57:17,599
but do you even know

870
00:57:18,280 --> 00:57:19,519
what a Great Emperor truly is?

871
00:57:21,120 --> 00:57:22,199
To me,

872
00:57:23,320 --> 00:57:25,359
you look more like a clown jumping on a stage.

873
00:57:27,840 --> 00:57:30,119
Then let me show you

874
00:57:30,440 --> 00:57:33,079
what the bearing of a Great Emperor really looks like.

875
00:58:13,720 --> 00:58:15,079
Isn’t that just a broken carriage?

876
00:58:15,360 --> 00:58:16,319
Yezi has one too,

877
00:58:16,320 --> 00:58:17,159
and it’s a Mercedes.

878
00:58:17,160 --> 00:58:18,160
Crush him!

879
00:58:18,560 --> 00:58:19,919
What nonsense are you lot spouting?

880
00:58:20,520 --> 00:58:21,919
My son possesses the bearing of a Great Emperor.

881
00:58:22,240 --> 00:58:22,639
You...

882
00:58:22,720 --> 00:58:24,079
You bunch of frogs at the bottom of a well,

883
00:58:24,320 --> 00:58:25,559
spouting such big talk.

884
00:58:27,920 --> 00:58:30,399
So you’re Wang Teng’s father.

885
00:58:31,160 --> 00:58:32,919
Well, my dad is Li Gang.

886
00:58:33,800 --> 00:58:34,759
Everyone knows

887
00:58:34,760 --> 00:58:36,119
my son is...

888
00:58:36,280 --> 00:58:36,839
Wait, no.

889
00:58:36,840 --> 00:58:37,840
My son

890
00:58:38,440 --> 00:58:39,759
is surnamed Wang,

891
00:58:39,760 --> 00:58:41,159
named Ba Gaozi Teng.

892
00:58:41,160 --> 00:58:42,679
He possesses the bearing of a Great Emperor.

893
00:58:45,640 --> 00:58:47,159
Is this all you’ve got?

894
00:58:47,200 --> 00:58:48,239
Not even close.

895
00:58:54,440 --> 00:58:55,759
This sword...

896
00:59:00,400 --> 00:59:01,919
Can you block it?

897
00:59:25,520 --> 00:59:26,719
My body is the Dao.

898
00:59:26,840 --> 00:59:27,999
All phenomena transform into the Dao.

899
00:59:33,360 --> 00:59:34,519
The inheritance of a Great Emperor

900
00:59:34,520 --> 00:59:36,479
is not something only you possess.

901
00:59:43,000 --> 00:59:44,519
The Solar True Scripture

902
00:59:45,200 --> 00:59:47,839
is the supreme secret art passed down by the Solar Holy Emperor.

903
00:59:49,280 --> 00:59:52,479
These two have nearly grasped their highest inheritances at the same time.

904
00:59:53,040 --> 00:59:54,599
This struggle for the Emperor’s path

905
00:59:54,640 --> 00:59:56,399
is becoming more and more interesting.

906
01:00:03,280 --> 01:00:04,280
Well met.

907
01:00:43,160 --> 01:00:44,559
Die!

908
01:00:53,240 --> 01:00:54,240
This sword

909
01:00:54,520 --> 01:00:55,520
shall cut you down.

910
01:00:57,040 --> 01:00:58,519
To wound me this badly,

911
01:00:59,120 --> 01:01:00,519
you can be proud of yourself.

912
01:01:04,920 --> 01:01:06,719
Eternal Exile.

913
01:01:13,920 --> 01:01:15,719
So earlier he was using his flesh body to resist,

914
01:01:15,880 --> 01:01:16,999
buying himself a slim chance.

915
01:01:17,520 --> 01:01:18,959
His true goal was this move all along.

916
01:01:20,120 --> 01:01:21,120
This battle

917
01:01:22,120 --> 01:01:23,799
ends here.

918
01:01:43,960 --> 01:01:45,359
It’s over.

919
01:01:47,960 --> 01:01:49,159
Miss Ziyue,

920
01:01:49,720 --> 01:01:51,239
now that the outcome is decided,

921
01:01:51,960 --> 01:01:53,719
you should give up, shouldn’t you?

922
01:01:55,720 --> 01:01:56,879
If this were before,

923
01:01:57,400 --> 01:01:59,239
I would’ve been sweating for him.

924
01:01:59,720 --> 01:02:00,720
But now...

925
01:02:01,160 --> 01:02:03,599
The real show has only just begun.

926
01:02:45,240 --> 01:02:46,799
Early Immortal Platform stage...

927
01:02:46,800 --> 01:02:48,759
How could you possibly break my Eternal Exile?

928
01:02:50,000 --> 01:02:51,679
Don’t you love arranging engagements?

929
01:02:52,600 --> 01:02:54,599
Then allow me to present this nine-colored gift.

930
01:02:56,080 --> 01:02:57,759
Please accept it.

931
01:03:03,520 --> 01:03:05,679
This is the divine flame from the ninth layer of the Fire Domain.

932
01:03:05,840 --> 01:03:06,839
Even an immortal

933
01:03:06,840 --> 01:03:07,999
would be burned to ashes.

934
01:03:08,280 --> 01:03:09,879
Let alone a Wang Ba Teng like you.

935
01:03:11,000 --> 01:03:12,399
What’s wrong? Too hot?

936
01:03:12,920 --> 01:03:14,599
Looks like your skin isn’t thick enough after all.

937
01:03:32,720 --> 01:03:33,879
Heavenly Emperor Sword.

938
01:03:34,000 --> 01:03:35,000
Slash!

939
01:03:37,720 --> 01:03:39,279
Returning it to you.

940
01:04:02,640 --> 01:04:03,640
Your Emperor’s path

941
01:04:04,000 --> 01:04:05,639
is nothing but illusion to me.

942
01:04:06,280 --> 01:04:06,959
I told you,

943
01:04:07,120 --> 01:04:08,120
I came here

944
01:04:08,200 --> 01:04:09,519
only to take her away.

945
01:04:09,920 --> 01:04:11,399
No one can stop me.

946
01:04:25,280 --> 01:04:27,439
Brother Ye is really trying to anger Wang Teng to death.

947
01:04:27,840 --> 01:04:29,119
So-called number one under heaven?

948
01:04:29,400 --> 01:04:30,400
All nonsense.

949
01:04:36,760 --> 01:04:38,479
With just you?

950
01:04:39,200 --> 01:04:40,959
You think you can make me lose?

951
01:04:42,240 --> 01:04:43,959
There’s something strange about Wang Teng.

952
01:04:43,960 --> 01:04:44,960
Don’t get close.

953
01:04:45,160 --> 01:04:46,639
Better to test him from a distance.

954
01:04:47,160 --> 01:04:47,599
That’s right.

955
01:04:47,920 --> 01:04:48,920
That gourd...

956
01:04:49,600 --> 01:04:51,999
Maybe I can imitate Lu Ya the Daoist from Investiture of the Gods.

957
01:04:52,520 --> 01:04:53,719
Do you have any more big moves?

958
01:04:53,720 --> 01:04:54,799
Feel free to use them all.

959
01:04:55,320 --> 01:04:57,079
Stop hiding them.

960
01:04:57,760 --> 01:04:59,159
If you still won’t come over,

961
01:05:00,200 --> 01:05:02,119
then don’t blame me for making the first move.

962
01:05:05,400 --> 01:05:06,400
Baby,

963
01:05:06,520 --> 01:05:07,559
please turn around.

964
01:05:19,920 --> 01:05:20,920
It actually worked.

965
01:05:25,320 --> 01:05:27,439
Why must the human race be so stubborn?

966
01:05:27,560 --> 01:05:29,479
Our goals are the same.

967
01:05:29,480 --> 01:05:30,919
Why not prosper together?

968
01:05:33,240 --> 01:05:34,240
Give it to me!

969
01:05:34,400 --> 01:05:35,919
Get lost!

970
01:05:58,440 --> 01:05:59,440
Teng’er...

971
01:06:00,600 --> 01:06:02,079
Do you really intend to push yourself

972
01:06:02,680 --> 01:06:04,199
this far?

973
01:06:04,720 --> 01:06:06,759
I was born to become Emperor.

974
01:06:07,440 --> 01:06:09,079
This is my destiny.

975
01:06:11,000 --> 01:06:12,479
My Emperor’s path,

976
01:06:12,720 --> 01:06:13,839
my Dao—

977
01:06:14,400 --> 01:06:16,439
how can it end here?

978
01:06:23,120 --> 01:06:24,559
I am the Northern Emperor.

979
01:06:26,200 --> 01:06:27,599
I have never lost once.

980
01:06:28,760 --> 01:06:30,599
And I absolutely cannot lose.

981
01:06:36,960 --> 01:06:37,960
What’s the meaning of this?

982
01:06:38,280 --> 01:06:39,280
Commit suicide?

983
01:06:39,720 --> 01:06:41,039
Severing Heaven

984
01:06:41,360 --> 01:06:42,439
is my Severing Dao Art.

985
01:06:42,440 --> 01:06:43,440
Sever the Dao!

986
01:06:44,080 --> 01:06:44,639
Ye Fan!

987
01:06:44,680 --> 01:06:46,039
Hurry up and finish off this Wang Ba Teng!

988
01:06:46,040 --> 01:06:47,319
Don’t wait for him to use his big move!

989
01:06:48,480 --> 01:06:49,679
Baby, please turn around.

990
01:06:51,600 --> 01:06:52,679
Baby, please kill.

991
01:06:53,800 --> 01:06:54,800
Baby, please chop him up.

992
01:06:56,160 --> 01:06:57,160
Baby...

993
01:07:01,360 --> 01:07:03,639
Sever my true self.

994
01:07:10,920 --> 01:07:12,079
His aura

995
01:07:12,720 --> 01:07:14,599
is more than twice as strong as before.

996
01:07:15,880 --> 01:07:17,519
The Northern Plains is not like the Southern Domain.

997
01:07:18,320 --> 01:07:19,559
For thousands of years,

998
01:07:20,000 --> 01:07:21,959
no Emperor Star has ever shone here.

999
01:07:24,560 --> 01:07:25,839
Teng’er’s Emperor path

1000
01:07:26,040 --> 01:07:28,399
carries the entire Northern Plains upon it.

1001
01:07:28,920 --> 01:07:30,759
This is his heavenly mandate.

1002
01:07:30,760 --> 01:07:31,760
And he

1003
01:07:32,120 --> 01:07:34,399
will surely shoulder this destiny.

1004
01:07:35,600 --> 01:07:36,839
Then let’s fight.

1005
01:07:44,400 --> 01:07:45,639
Word Secret.

1006
01:07:46,280 --> 01:07:47,280
Rise!

1007
01:07:48,360 --> 01:07:49,360
Don’t even think about it!

1008
01:07:51,160 --> 01:07:52,160
Too late.

1009
01:08:14,520 --> 01:08:15,839
Found you.

1010
01:08:18,040 --> 01:08:19,040
Not good!

1011
01:08:32,920 --> 01:08:33,920
Word Secret.

1012
01:08:34,200 --> 01:08:35,200
Refine the primordial spirit.

1013
01:08:35,360 --> 01:08:36,719
It can make divine sense immortal.

1014
01:08:37,200 --> 01:08:38,719
If cultivated to a certain level,

1015
01:08:39,080 --> 01:08:40,839
it can glimpse a sliver of the future.

1016
01:08:41,320 --> 01:08:43,119
I won’t give you that chance.

1017
01:08:50,280 --> 01:08:51,839
I’ve already seen through you.

1018
01:08:52,800 --> 01:08:55,039
Your moves are full of openings.

1019
01:08:55,480 --> 01:08:56,919
How could you possibly defeat me?

1020
01:09:00,560 --> 01:09:01,999
All paths converge as one.

1021
01:09:02,120 --> 01:09:03,199
Two secrets united.

1022
01:09:04,600 --> 01:09:05,719
Can you break this?

1023
01:09:06,320 --> 01:09:06,919
This is...

1024
01:09:07,160 --> 01:09:08,319
What exactly did you do?

1025
01:09:09,000 --> 01:09:10,000
As expected.

1026
01:09:10,040 --> 01:09:11,679
The Word Secret allows one to glimpse a corner of the future
before striking.

1027
01:09:11,800 --> 01:09:12,919
Thanks to your powerful primordial spirit,

1028
01:09:13,400 --> 01:09:15,039
the Word Secret primarily cultivates the spirit.

1029
01:09:15,080 --> 01:09:17,039
Competing with me in primordial spirit?

1030
01:09:17,400 --> 01:09:18,839
You’re courting death.

1031
01:09:19,760 --> 01:09:20,760
Die!

1032
01:09:27,840 --> 01:09:28,840
I know.

1033
01:09:28,960 --> 01:09:29,960
In terms of primordial spirit alone,

1034
01:09:30,000 --> 01:09:31,000
you are indeed very strong.

1035
01:09:31,680 --> 01:09:33,119
But Source Heaven Divine Art

1036
01:09:33,400 --> 01:09:34,599
is more than enough to suppress you.

1037
01:09:41,800 --> 01:09:42,879
How is this possible?

1038
01:09:43,440 --> 01:09:44,440
Your Source Art...

1039
01:09:53,200 --> 01:09:54,279
You rely on a single secret

1040
01:09:54,600 --> 01:09:56,199
and dare call yourself unrivaled under heaven.

1041
01:09:56,800 --> 01:09:57,800
But don’t forget,

1042
01:09:58,280 --> 01:09:59,679
I cultivate four secrets.

1043
01:10:04,160 --> 01:10:05,799
Four secrets united.

1044
01:10:06,320 --> 01:10:07,719
This will send you on your way.

1045
01:10:24,040 --> 01:10:24,399
Combine!

1046
01:10:26,040 --> 01:10:26,879
Well done, Yezi!

1047
01:10:27,040 --> 01:10:28,199
Well done!

1048
01:10:34,360 --> 01:10:37,319
Die!

1049
01:11:07,920 --> 01:11:09,359
Why...

1050
01:11:19,360 --> 01:11:21,959
Why did you win?

1051
01:11:29,200 --> 01:11:30,200
You old bastard!

1052
01:11:30,800 --> 01:11:31,879
You finally can’t sit still anymore.

1053
01:11:31,880 --> 01:11:33,119
This is wrong.

1054
01:11:33,400 --> 01:11:35,159
This is definitely a mistake.

1055
01:11:35,480 --> 01:11:37,399
[Void Mirror — Supreme Imperial Weapon]
I won’t allow this!

1056
01:11:37,423 --> 01:11:37,779
[Void Mirror — Supreme Imperial Weapon]

1057
01:11:38,680 --> 01:11:39,359
Eighth Ancestor!

1058
01:11:39,360 --> 01:11:40,360
What are you doing?

1059
01:11:40,480 --> 01:11:41,480
Eighth Ancestor, think carefully!

1060
01:11:41,720 --> 01:11:43,799
Clan rules strictly forbid the reckless use of Imperial weapons!

1061
01:11:44,680 --> 01:11:45,680
Ye Fan!

1062
01:11:45,920 --> 01:11:47,679
You intrude upon my Ji Family’s sacred land,

1063
01:11:47,680 --> 01:11:49,039
slay my Ji Family’s chosen son-in-law,

1064
01:11:49,240 --> 01:11:50,679
and bewitch my Ji Family’s brightest pearl.

1065
01:11:50,960 --> 01:11:52,599
Three crimes combined,

1066
01:11:52,640 --> 01:11:54,039
not even a hundred deaths could atone!

1067
01:11:54,560 --> 01:11:56,079
Today, this ancestor

1068
01:11:56,080 --> 01:11:58,719
shall borrow the Void Mirror to purge all vermin

1069
01:11:58,920 --> 01:12:00,359
and set the record straight.

1070
01:12:07,000 --> 01:12:08,639
What a perfect “three crimes combined.”

1071
01:12:09,000 --> 01:12:09,599
Old thief,

1072
01:12:09,960 --> 01:12:11,719
why don’t you use the Void Mirror to look at yourself?

1073
01:12:12,040 --> 01:12:13,479
See that hideous face of yours

1074
01:12:13,480 --> 01:12:15,079
and how it tarnishes this Imperial weapon.

1075
01:12:16,880 --> 01:12:19,319
You know nothing

1076
01:12:19,800 --> 01:12:21,359
of a true Imperial weapon’s power.

1077
01:12:27,000 --> 01:12:28,319
Did you really think

1078
01:12:28,880 --> 01:12:31,039
I would have no way to resist an Imperial weapon?

1079
01:12:40,280 --> 01:12:40,879
Brother...

1080
01:12:41,080 --> 01:12:42,679
What exactly is that coffin?

1081
01:12:43,040 --> 01:12:44,040
It’s so terrifying.

1082
01:12:44,280 --> 01:12:45,919
The terror doesn’t lie in the bronze coffin itself,

1083
01:12:46,720 --> 01:12:48,359
but in what sleeps inside it.

1084
01:12:48,912 --> 01:12:50,333
[Chaos Qi]

1085
01:12:52,400 --> 01:12:53,400
This bronze coffin

1086
01:12:53,480 --> 01:12:55,039
actually managed to withstand the Void Mirror.

1087
01:12:57,840 --> 01:12:59,199
All Ji Family elders,

1088
01:12:59,440 --> 01:13:01,239
join me in activating the Void Mirror

1089
01:13:01,360 --> 01:13:02,439
to suppress and kill Ye Fan!

1090
01:13:02,960 --> 01:13:03,960
Fellow elders,

1091
01:13:04,200 --> 01:13:05,919
the Eighth Ancestor has gone mad and violated clan rules.

1092
01:13:06,280 --> 01:13:07,359
Anyone who helps him

1093
01:13:07,800 --> 01:13:09,439
is no different from a traitor to our clan!

1094
01:13:17,520 --> 01:13:18,520
What?

1095
01:13:18,800 --> 01:13:20,519
The Imperial weapon is resisting!

1096
01:13:23,720 --> 01:13:24,720
Break!

1097
01:13:46,480 --> 01:13:47,719
After all that scheming,

1098
01:13:48,720 --> 01:13:50,359
I still couldn’t defeat

1099
01:13:51,480 --> 01:13:53,239
an ant.

1100
01:14:01,200 --> 01:14:02,359
The Eighth Ancestor has lost.

1101
01:14:02,680 --> 01:14:04,159
This bronze coffin is terrifyingly powerful.

1102
01:14:04,240 --> 01:14:05,759
It can even contend with the Void Mirror.

1103
01:14:06,120 --> 01:14:07,359
Serves the Eighth Ancestor right.

1104
01:14:07,560 --> 01:14:08,879
Even the Ji Family won’t help him now.

1105
01:14:09,360 --> 01:14:10,360
In the end, relying on him alone,

1106
01:14:10,680 --> 01:14:12,919
he naturally couldn’t unleash the Imperial weapon’s full power.

1107
01:14:14,120 --> 01:14:15,999
Using a coffin as a weapon...

1108
01:14:16,280 --> 01:14:16,879
Brother Ye,

1109
01:14:17,120 --> 01:14:18,759
you really are one of a kind.

1110
01:14:20,200 --> 01:14:21,119
From now on,

1111
01:14:21,120 --> 01:14:21,879
in the entire Eastern Wasteland,

1112
01:14:22,120 --> 01:14:23,279
who would still dare touch you?

1113
01:14:53,480 --> 01:14:54,599
Ye Fan...

1114
01:14:55,080 --> 01:14:56,199
Thank you.

1115
01:14:56,840 --> 01:14:57,879
Thank you.

1116
01:14:59,040 --> 01:15:00,040
Ziyue.

1117
01:15:00,720 --> 01:15:01,720
From today onward,

1118
01:15:02,840 --> 01:15:04,719
no one can ever force you to do anything again.

1119
01:15:13,960 --> 01:15:15,239
That outfit you’re wearing today...

1120
01:15:17,960 --> 01:15:18,960
looks really good on you.

1121
01:15:22,480 --> 01:15:23,480
Teng’er...

1122
01:15:24,560 --> 01:15:25,560
Teng’er!

1123
01:15:27,800 --> 01:15:29,079
Father will take you back to the Northern Plains.

1124
01:15:30,400 --> 01:15:32,039
No matter the cost,

1125
01:15:33,200 --> 01:15:35,239
Father will do everything to save you.

1126
01:15:36,520 --> 01:15:37,359
I lost...

1127
01:15:38,640 --> 01:15:39,959
I actually lost.

1128
01:15:43,800 --> 01:15:44,800
Why...

1129
01:15:45,480 --> 01:15:47,119
Why did it turn out like this?

1130
01:15:49,120 --> 01:15:50,120
No...

1131
01:15:51,360 --> 01:15:52,679
I will not lose.

1132
01:15:58,640 --> 01:15:59,640
I...

1133
01:15:59,800 --> 01:16:01,359
absolutely cannot

1134
01:16:02,080 --> 01:16:03,719
lose!

1135
01:16:04,680 --> 01:16:05,680
What’s happening?

1136
01:16:06,160 --> 01:16:07,160
What is this?

1137
01:16:08,560 --> 01:16:09,560
Teng’er...

1138
01:16:28,200 --> 01:16:31,519
Human, accept my power.

1139
01:16:31,720 --> 01:16:35,079
This is not enslavement, but fusion.

1140
01:16:35,480 --> 01:16:37,839
This is the true meaning of mutual prosperity.

1141
01:16:38,160 --> 01:16:39,319
And you

1142
01:16:39,400 --> 01:16:42,919
shall become the ruler of this new order.

1143
01:16:43,360 --> 01:16:44,919
This aura does not belong to the current era.

1144
01:17:23,320 --> 01:17:24,959
It’s the aura of a Primordial Supreme.

1145
01:17:25,440 --> 01:17:26,639
This Eternal Blue Gold

1146
01:17:26,880 --> 01:17:28,679
was never any Great Emperor inheritance at all.

1147
01:17:29,080 --> 01:17:30,119
It’s an evil relic.

1148
01:17:30,240 --> 01:17:31,319
We cannot let it appear in the world.

1149
01:17:31,640 --> 01:17:32,799
Quickly exterminate this person!

1150
01:18:00,160 --> 01:18:02,199
The heart’s domain shall perish.

1151
01:18:02,640 --> 01:18:04,439
Resentment fills the ends of the earth.

1152
01:18:04,800 --> 01:18:06,799
Our ancestors tasted both warmth and cold.

1153
01:18:07,160 --> 01:18:09,399
I have come to continue the annals of history.

1154
01:18:33,120 --> 01:18:36,119
Wang Teng truly was the optimal choice for our race.

1155
01:18:36,560 --> 01:18:38,319
He actually triggered the hidden Primordial Supreme aura

1156
01:18:38,320 --> 01:18:40,599
within the Eternal Blue Gold.

1157
01:18:41,160 --> 01:18:42,479
From today onward,

1158
01:18:42,760 --> 01:18:43,999
the Northern Emperor Wang Teng

1159
01:18:44,000 --> 01:18:46,599
shall be our race’s representative in the Northern Dipper.

1160
01:18:46,920 --> 01:18:47,920
Correct.

1161
01:18:48,040 --> 01:18:49,759
He will surely come to understand

1162
01:18:50,200 --> 01:18:51,799
that mutual prosperity with our race

1163
01:18:51,920 --> 01:18:54,879
is the only chance for the human race to survive.

1164
01:18:58,160 --> 01:18:59,799
We will not allow

1165
01:19:00,320 --> 01:19:03,359
the human race to produce another Great Emperor of their own.

1166
01:19:08,360 --> 01:19:09,679
Void...

1167
01:19:10,800 --> 01:19:12,559
For over a hundred thousand years,

1168
01:19:13,800 --> 01:19:16,639
the human race will ultimately be ruled by our race.

1169
01:19:17,840 --> 01:19:20,239
The Northern Dipper shall become our hunting ground.

1170
01:19:22,360 --> 01:19:24,919
You shortened your lifespan and gave up eternal life.

1171
01:19:25,360 --> 01:19:26,360
Was it worth it?

1172
01:19:27,080 --> 01:19:29,559
The desolate ancient Ji Family will cease to exist.

1173
01:19:31,720 --> 01:19:33,479
The era you opened

1174
01:19:35,120 --> 01:19:37,159
shall be ended by me.

1175
01:19:45,800 --> 01:19:46,399
You...

1176
01:19:46,800 --> 01:19:48,879
you deranged demonic creature!

1177
01:19:49,120 --> 01:19:50,519
The Origin Spirit Body...

1178
01:19:51,080 --> 01:19:52,519
I see.

1179
01:19:53,160 --> 01:19:56,319
This can accelerate my recovery several times over.

1180
01:20:13,240 --> 01:20:15,039
Annoying pest.

1181
01:20:15,040 --> 01:20:16,279
I almost forgot about you.

1182
01:20:17,800 --> 01:20:18,800
Wang Teng...

1183
01:20:19,040 --> 01:20:20,519
Are you still yourself right now?

1184
01:20:23,280 --> 01:20:24,519
Does it make any difference?

1185
01:20:42,640 --> 01:20:43,640
Ye Fan...

1186
01:20:54,200 --> 01:20:57,199
As long as I can stand at the peak and achieve the Emperor’s path,

1187
01:20:57,640 --> 01:20:59,679
I can also prosper together with the strong.

1188
01:21:00,280 --> 01:21:01,559
The human race is weak.

1189
01:21:01,920 --> 01:21:03,919
Only by merging with other races can we succeed.

1190
01:21:13,840 --> 01:21:15,959
Your vision is too narrow.

1191
01:21:16,480 --> 01:21:17,799
Only by letting go

1192
01:21:18,240 --> 01:21:20,079
can one become invincible.

1193
01:21:28,560 --> 01:21:30,719
You underestimate the human race too much.

1194
01:21:35,440 --> 01:21:36,440
Even if I fall,

1195
01:21:38,040 --> 01:21:39,040
in the future

1196
01:21:39,720 --> 01:21:41,719
someone will surely crush you.

1197
01:21:48,440 --> 01:21:50,439
Then I’ll crush you first.

1198
01:22:16,480 --> 01:22:17,879
Void...

1199
01:22:18,480 --> 01:22:20,959
Do you really think

1200
01:22:20,960 --> 01:22:22,559
a mere wisp of Imperial might can stop me?

1201
01:22:28,840 --> 01:22:30,959
Walking the Emperor’s path isn’t what matters.

1202
01:22:31,880 --> 01:22:33,479
Walking your own path

1203
01:22:34,360 --> 01:22:36,839
is the true road to invincibility.

1204
01:22:37,640 --> 01:22:40,159
If you abandon even your identity as a human,

1205
01:22:40,840 --> 01:22:42,799
then everything becomes an illusion.

1206
01:22:43,560 --> 01:22:44,799
Very well.

1207
01:22:45,880 --> 01:22:47,399
Then with this strike,

1208
01:22:48,040 --> 01:22:49,799
let all living beings witness

1209
01:22:50,520 --> 01:22:51,799
my rebirth.

1210
01:23:31,000 --> 01:23:32,759
A small accomplishment Saint Body is rare.

1211
01:23:33,640 --> 01:23:34,999
If you’re willing to submit,

1212
01:23:35,720 --> 01:23:37,479
I can immediately send you

1213
01:23:37,800 --> 01:23:39,919
to anywhere you wish to go.

1214
01:23:46,560 --> 01:23:47,959
With power like yours,

1215
01:23:48,600 --> 01:23:51,439
you still dare speak of things even a God King cannot do.

1216
01:23:52,360 --> 01:23:53,439
Isn’t that laughable?

1217
01:23:55,960 --> 01:23:58,159
As long as I use the Origin Spirit Body to accelerate my revival,

1218
01:23:58,880 --> 01:24:01,439
the might of an Ancient Emperor will spread across the universe.

1219
01:24:02,560 --> 01:24:04,439
And she won’t die.

1220
01:24:04,560 --> 01:24:06,359
You can go home right away.

1221
01:24:09,600 --> 01:24:10,600
Idiot.

1222
01:24:21,160 --> 01:24:23,879
Is that your condition?

1223
01:24:24,680 --> 01:24:25,999
Not bad.

1224
01:24:28,240 --> 01:24:30,119
Delusion.

1225
01:24:34,480 --> 01:24:36,239
No matter how great the benefit,

1226
01:24:36,560 --> 01:24:37,919
or how small the price,

1227
01:24:38,200 --> 01:24:39,119
I still

1228
01:24:39,120 --> 01:24:40,519
refuse.

1229
01:24:52,360 --> 01:24:53,799
Principles

1230
01:24:55,760 --> 01:24:58,519
are not meant to be traded.

1231
01:26:48,600 --> 01:26:49,600
Teng’er...

1232
01:26:50,160 --> 01:26:51,160
What was that just now?

1233
01:26:52,920 --> 01:26:53,920
Father will take you back.

1234
01:26:54,640 --> 01:26:55,640
We’ll find that old crane.

1235
01:26:57,480 --> 01:26:58,719
You’ll be fine.

1236
01:27:01,000 --> 01:27:02,000
Teng’er...

1237
01:27:02,840 --> 01:27:03,639
Teng’er!

1238
01:27:04,000 --> 01:27:05,359
What happened just now?

1239
01:27:06,120 --> 01:27:08,039
It seemed like the figure of our clan’s Great Emperor.

1240
01:27:08,480 --> 01:27:11,439
And that dream-like space earlier...

1241
01:27:12,080 --> 01:27:13,239
Did you all see it?

1242
01:27:15,400 --> 01:27:17,919
It must have been the collision of a Great Emperor’s and a Supreme’s imprint.

1243
01:27:18,400 --> 01:27:20,239
It fully awakened the power of the Word Secret,

1244
01:27:21,200 --> 01:27:22,879
deducing a future that does not exist

1245
01:27:23,520 --> 01:27:25,439
and striking down an unknown threat.

1246
01:27:27,360 --> 01:27:28,839
The Void Emperor...

1247
01:27:28,840 --> 01:27:30,119
was truly powerful.

1248
01:27:30,440 --> 01:27:33,919
The enemy who shortened his lifespan by three thousand years back then

1249
01:27:34,360 --> 01:27:35,799
must have been terrifying.

1250
01:27:35,800 --> 01:27:38,519
Thankfully Purple Mountain was once the Dao field of the Unbeginning Great Emperor.

1251
01:27:39,040 --> 01:27:40,799
At its center lies the Unbeginning Bell.

1252
01:27:42,040 --> 01:27:43,040
The Unbeginning Bell...

1253
01:27:43,200 --> 01:27:44,319
Why is it ringing now?

1254
01:27:54,280 --> 01:27:57,319
Seas turn to dust over tens of thousands of autumns.

1255
01:27:57,840 --> 01:28:01,199
The Dao transforms, yellowed hair brings worry of longevity.

1256
01:28:02,000 --> 01:28:04,479
One dream spans several thousand years.

1257
01:28:05,000 --> 01:28:08,759
The immortal path is rugged—where does one wander?

1258
01:28:08,760 --> 01:28:10,959
I wonder which exalted one has arrived

1259
01:28:10,960 --> 01:28:12,279
at my Ji Family.

1260
01:28:14,040 --> 01:28:16,520
I am the last successor of the Unbeginning.

1261
01:28:17,840 --> 01:28:20,039
Hearing that a Saint Body exists in this era,

1262
01:28:20,720 --> 01:28:22,039
I have come specially to meet him.

1263
01:28:22,280 --> 01:28:23,719
He actually came for the Saint Body.

1264
01:28:25,360 --> 01:28:27,239
I wish to take him as my disciple

1265
01:28:28,000 --> 01:28:29,000
and pass on

1266
01:28:29,640 --> 01:28:31,199
the Unbeginning Scripture.

1267
01:28:31,640 --> 01:28:32,399
Heavens!

1268
01:28:32,640 --> 01:28:33,719
The Unbeginning inheritance!

1269
01:28:34,520 --> 01:28:36,119
What a heaven-defying opportunity!

1270
01:28:36,440 --> 01:28:37,440
Yezi,

1271
01:28:37,560 --> 01:28:38,560
this opportunity is incredible!

1272
01:28:45,640 --> 01:28:46,640
Dead dog,

1273
01:28:47,320 --> 01:28:48,320
even the Unbeginning Great Emperor

1274
01:28:48,560 --> 01:28:49,879
would be angered back to life by you.

1275
01:29:04,600 --> 01:29:06,439
The Void Emperor had a lifespan of ten thousand years

1276
01:29:06,760 --> 01:29:07,799
but only lived seven thousand.

1277
01:29:09,040 --> 01:29:11,479
It was because after battling the nine great Saint Bodies across the heavens,

1278
01:29:11,840 --> 01:29:12,840
he bled all the way,

1279
01:29:13,480 --> 01:29:15,199
holding up this world alone.

1280
01:29:16,720 --> 01:29:17,799
The so-called Emperor’s path

1281
01:29:18,400 --> 01:29:19,400
is not about being undefeated,

1282
01:29:20,120 --> 01:29:21,120
but about protection.

1283
01:29:22,920 --> 01:29:23,920
Throughout the ages,

1284
01:29:24,480 --> 01:29:26,319
which of the Great Emperors truly remembered

1285
01:29:26,840 --> 01:29:29,039
did not shoulder the tribulations of the world

1286
01:29:29,400 --> 01:29:31,519
and safeguard the peace of this land?

1287
01:29:33,280 --> 01:29:34,280
The Emperor’s path

1288
01:29:34,640 --> 01:29:36,599
has never been a ladder of the strong devouring the weak,

1289
01:29:36,920 --> 01:29:38,799
nor a stairway to enslave the world.

1290
01:29:39,440 --> 01:29:40,440
Becoming Emperor

1291
01:29:40,720 --> 01:29:42,239
is not about reaching the peak

1292
01:29:42,640 --> 01:29:44,319
and commanding with a single word.

1293
01:29:45,960 --> 01:29:47,199
It is about standing at that summit

1294
01:29:47,960 --> 01:29:50,199
and shouldering the mission

1295
01:29:50,600 --> 01:29:52,439
to protect the vast rivers and mountains
and all living beings.

1296
01:29:54,902 --> 01:29:56,902
[Don’t go away—there’s a bonus scene]

1297
01:32:22,800 --> 01:32:23,800
Divine Son.

1298
01:32:24,440 --> 01:32:26,839
In a future that does not exist,
the Saint Body defeated Wang Teng.

1299
01:32:27,800 --> 01:32:29,519
We were unable to turn that illusion into reality.

1300
01:32:29,880 --> 01:32:31,399
It consumed a Supreme’s technique.

1301
01:32:32,040 --> 01:32:33,079
Please punish me.

1302
01:32:35,080 --> 01:32:35,479
No.

1303
01:32:35,960 --> 01:32:37,759
You have already completed your task.

1304
01:32:38,920 --> 01:32:41,559
Hiding the true objective was the key to the entire scheme.

1305
01:32:42,920 --> 01:32:45,479
Wang Teng carries the inheritance of the Chaos Ancient Great Emperor.

1306
01:32:45,800 --> 01:32:47,159
He seeks to become Emperor through defeat.

1307
01:32:48,160 --> 01:32:49,799
How could someone walking an undefeated path

1308
01:32:50,240 --> 01:32:51,919
possibly win?

1309
01:32:52,480 --> 01:32:54,959
Although the Saint Body did not perform as expected,

1310
01:32:55,440 --> 01:32:58,639
from the moment Wang Teng agreed to propose marriage to the Ji Family,

1311
01:32:59,160 --> 01:33:00,879
we had already succeeded.

1312
01:33:02,240 --> 01:33:04,799
Our race’s aura infiltrating the Ji Family

1313
01:33:05,320 --> 01:33:07,199
was merely a probe

1314
01:33:07,480 --> 01:33:09,839
to see if the human Great Emperors left any hidden countermeasures against us.

1315
01:33:10,960 --> 01:33:13,999
And now, after such open provocation,

1316
01:33:14,400 --> 01:33:19,079
the human Great Emperors only passively activated their imprints.

1317
01:33:19,920 --> 01:33:21,399
With this,

1318
01:33:22,040 --> 01:33:24,759
we can begin advancing to the next stage of the plan

1319
01:33:25,200 --> 01:33:27,799
and scheme to unify the ten thousand races.

1320
01:33:52,640 --> 01:33:54,159
Patriarch of the Wang Family,

1321
01:33:54,280 --> 01:33:55,839
why do you look so troubled?

1322
01:34:06,760 --> 01:34:07,919
Zi Tianfeng...

1323
01:34:11,840 --> 01:34:13,199
The Wang Family’s path

1324
01:34:13,800 --> 01:34:15,919
has not yet reached its end.

1325
01:34:21,520 --> 01:34:22,599
What do you mean?

1326
01:34:22,623 --> 01:34:45,323
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

